data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home featuring three bedrooms, two baths, and a den in the centrally located community of Crossing Creek Village.  Tucked away in the back of the community no through traffic and soon to be completed access to 44th Ave E.  This open floorplan is cozy yet spacious with two bedrooms and a guest bath to the front of the home.  As you pass through the foyer you are greeted by the great room and gorgeous kitchen which is great for family time or entertaining guests.  Kitchen features stainless appliances, tile backsplash, endless granite countertops and a closet pantry.  There are two areas which can be used as a dining area or dinette.  The master suite has a glass shower, garden tub, dual vanities, and a huge walk in closet.  Outdoor living was not spared with a covered lanai and beautiful backyard with no rear neighbors.  Crossing Creek Village has no CDD fees, centrally located with easy access to shopping, dining, I-75, and access to the beaches via 44th Ave extension.  Come and see this great home and make it yours today!
